document_data.name: Braundlae
document_data.mainbody: '''Braundlae''' was a waitress at [[Braundlae's Best]] beneath the [[Roving Dragon]] in [[Suzail]], [[Cormyr]].
document_data.Allies: She was acquainted with [[Glarasteer Rhauligan]], who she referred to as "Rhauly".
